title: Rocket City Rednecks
description: Get ready to blow up some stereotypes when Neil deGrasse Tyson meets aerospace engineer and Rocket City Redneck Travis S. Taylor. Co-hosted by Chuck Nice and guest starring Bill Nye the Science Guy.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
